(42, 20, 11, 44, 7, 52, 52, 'beat him also, and entreated him shamefully', 'Persecution of God''s Messengers', 'This connection highlights the theme of persecution faced by God''s servants. Both passages emphasize the mistreatment of those sent by God, with Luke referencing the beating of servants and Acts recalling the persecution of prophets.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 20, 11, 52, 2, 2, 2, NULL, 'Suffering and Shameful Treatment', 'Both passages emphasize being ''shamefully entreated'' and suffering for their message. This connection highlights the shared experience of rejection and mistreatment faced by God''s messengers.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
